Class Student

java.lang.Object
Student

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
This class is the abstract parent class for the different types of Students.

    • compareTo

      public int compareTo​(java.lang.Object obj)
      This method will compare two Students. Comparisons start with first name and then last name.
      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable
      Parameters:
      obj - is the Student that needs to be compared to the current Student
      Returns:
      0 if the first and last name are the same, 1 if this greater than obj and -1 if this less than obj
